product_name: Cycle Dog Earth Friendly Pick-Up Bags
long_description: The Cycle Dog Earth Friendly pick-up bags are a thoughtful and biodegradable way to dispose of your best friend's waste. Corn- and plant-based bags decompose through natural microbial decay when buried or placed in your backyard compost. Bags will decompose in 10 - 45 days in a controlled composting environment. Help keep the your community clean by always picking up after your pet. Includes 6 rolls; 12 bags per roll.
